data.description: Wonderful Family Home in the heart of Citrus Heights. Single story 4 bed 2 bath home with spacious living areas and great flow. Unique U-Shaped design allows for separation of bedrooms and living area without feeling closed off. The remodeled kitchen overlooks a cozy family room with a skylight and floor to ceiling window that let the natural light pour in, it is truly the heart of the home. The kitchen boasts beautiful laminate flooring and modern appliances, Corian type countertops and plenty of cabinets and counter space for the serious chefs. Separate family and formal living room with its own cozy fireplace are perfect for entertaining and hosting those big holiday get togethers. The Master Bedroom opens onto the tranquil backyard patio.   Conveniently located, easy freeway access and only 20 minutes from downtown, 1 mile from Mercy San Juan Medical Center, and less than a quarter mile from public transit with a varity of shopping, schools, parks and restaurants nearby. This home has been loved and well maintained and is ready for a lucky new owner to call it home.
